UX requirements:
- Show “Recommended every payday + 1 day”
- Show safe-to-spend after transfers
- Allow check-off when user completes manual transfer
- Allow user to adjust transfer amount
- Carry missed/short transfers into next recommendation
- Show what each transfer funds
- Keep the user focused on quarterly review, not daily budget management

Main value proposition:
BudgetWise becomes an automated cash-flow operating system. It helps users avoid overdrafts, fund bills before due dates, save consistently, and know what is truly safe to spend without checking the budget constantly.
